::Prowl::

Pain shot through Prowl as his broken wing was moved aside, the 
Maximal seeing through scanners that Iron Raptor was standing over 
him. Irrationaly, he cursed himself for being stupid enough to 
collide with a tree branch.

There was no feeling as Iron Raptor dug a claw into his neck, other 
than the sickening one of some of his insides being pused aside. Whe 
place where Iron Raptor had incerted her claw was still in the numb 
region.
